-- Edge case: special characters in yield values

cell quotes
  yield text = "She said \"hello\" to 'them'"

cell unicode
  yield emoji = "Hello 🌍 World"

cell json-val
  yield data = {"key": "value", "count": 42}

cell consumer
  given quotes.text
  given unicode.emoji
  given json-val.data
  yield summary
  ---
  Concatenate these three values separated by " | ": «text», «emoji», «data». Return the concatenated string.
  ---
